#Minimal Fe BCC to verify OMP_NUM_THREADS is respected
lattice body-centered Cubic 5.42
ion-species GBRV/$ID_lda.uspp
elec-cutoff 15 75
elec-ex-corr lda
ion Fe  0 0 0  0
kpoint-folding 1 1 1
elec-smearing Fermi 0.01
spintype z-spin
elec-initial-magnetization 3 no
electronic-SCF nIterations 3
dump End None
